{"tid":2489118,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國大學要打毒針先可以返學","createTime":"2021-04-14T17:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T18:36:32.000Z","uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46829dc7c2821cfc2a15cb3755af88afd8a77668","tid":2489118,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"有打疫苗才准返校 美國多所大學跟進 強制規定惹議<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對於暑假過後的新學年規畫，越來越多大學強制規定學生必須完成新冠疫苗接種，今秋才能返回校園；不過，CNBC新聞報導，家長之間普遍仍對疫苗存疑。<br />\n<br />\n過去幾天裡，杜克大學(Duke University)、布朗大學(Brown University)、東北大學(Northeastern University)、聖母大學(University of Notre Dame)與雪城大學(Syracuse University)等校，陸續宣布今秋開學時，學生必須在第一天上學之前完成疫苗接種。<br />\n<br />\n康乃爾大學(Cornell University)、羅格斯大學(Rutgers University)之前已宣布，2021年秋季班開學時，將全面要求學生施打疫苗；美國大學院所協會(AACU)主席派斯奎瑞拉(Lynn Pasquerella)表示，越來越多大學可望加入全面要求學生打疫苗的。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，今秋新學期開始時是否應該要求學生接種疫苗，從法律角度來看學校是否有權強制要求學生打疫苗？大學之間看法不一。<br />\n<br />\n康乃爾大學、布朗大學等希望透過疫苗施打讓校園達到群體免疫(herd immunity)目標，好讓教室、宿舍的防疫規定得以鬆綁。<br />\n<br />\n康乃爾大學校長波拉克(Martha Pollack)及教務長考里科夫(Michael Kotlikoff)在聲明中表示，學生若因健康因素或宗教信仰而無法施打疫苗，校方願意通融，但目前規畫是今秋的校園與教室裡，將有著絕大多數已完成疫苗接種的人，如此可以大幅減低病毒傳染。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，某些學校則把是否打疫苗的決定權留給學生，部分人士則認為，學校沒有法律權限能強迫學生接種新冠疫苗；維吉尼亞理工學院(Virginia Tech)校方主管便指出，聯邦食品暨藥物管理局(FDA)只核准疫苗的緊急使用授權，尚未全面授權，因此學校無權強迫學生打疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n要求學生今秋必須全面完成疫苗施打的東北大學等校則認為，學校在法理基礎上絕對站得住腳。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，大學因為某些傳染疾病而要求學生打疫苗，在過去便有前例，加州法院2020年判決指出，加州大學(University of California)旗下學校，可要求學生施打流感疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6813/5384482?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-cate5-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6813%2F5384482%3Ffrom%3Dudn-ch1_breaknews-1-cate5-news&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sPch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=0b59cbc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6813/5384482?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-cate5-news</a>"},{"pid":"92c45ac35d8fb13674f199851597244bc55d3c9a","tid":2489118,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a96da17c4f14223f2f2f265bee8c057bfb0eeb7","tid":2489118,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fca3d059cc1f7a33e2ea086fa7e18f36247f75a","tid":2489118,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:47:18.000Z","msg":"要打生死針先可以返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a2544405416210fbba8d336392f571807b38b4","tid":2489118,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"被natural selection<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4c989040ab3e8f93b322955fea479eae9d7a9e","tid":2489118,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"（有班）連登仔：盡公民責任有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed7d599638bbec6862afa14abfe9b17705111c6","tid":2489118,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"剩係計情況都唔撚同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2c97678135dc57b242fa13e06a80e6981f3308","tid":2489118,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:54:51.000Z","msg":"打完毒針個樣　＞＞　<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d90bd4f338556dd7372aaa5f4740